headline: Equity Residential: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The Chicago-based real estate investment trust said it had funds from operations of $399.2 million, or $1.02 per share, in the period. The average estimate of 10 analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for funds from operations of $1.02 per share. Funds from operations is a closely watched measure in the REIT industry.
